Notes on what this license does and does not cover:
  - device-samsung-a31/APKBUILD builds the GPL-2.0 downstream kernel from
    github.com/Galaxy-MT6768/android_kernel_samsung_mt6768. That kernel keeps
    its own license; this repo only ships the build recipe and config notes.
  - connsys/mtinit.c and connsys/mtdaemon.c are derived from openmttools
    (gitlab.com/Dahrkael/openmttools); see that project for its license.
  - No proprietary vendor firmware is included. Harvest it from your own device.
